==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sobbing
<hw>Sob"bing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A series of short,
convulsive inspirations, the glottis being suddenly closed so that
little or no air enters into the lungs.</def> <-- a less intense form of
crying -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sober</ent>⟦br⟧
